OL,3,C'Shocking' moment van driver
OL,4,Cdistracted on phone crashes into
OL,5,Cbroken-down car
OL,7,FDashcam footage and video inside the
OL,8,Fvehicle shows the moment a van driver,
OL,9,Fdistracted on his phone, crashed into
OL,10,Fa car that had broken down in Sussex.
OL,12,FNathan Cole was travelling at 72mph,
OL,13,F12mph over the speed limit for his
OL,14,Fvehicle, and struck the car that had
OL,15,Fstopped on the A27 dual carriageway at
OL,16,FSouthbourne in December 2023.
OL,18,FHe later admitted he had been checking
OL,19,Fsocial media on his phone before he
OL,20,Fcrashed.
