OL,7,FThe driver of the car that was hit, a
OL,8,Fman in his 60s from Hampshire, was
OL,9,Frushed to hospital in a critical
OL,10,Fcondition.
OL,12,FHe remained in a coma over the
OL,13,FChristmas period, and had to have his
OL,14,Fleg amputated.
OL,16,FCole, 29, of Denton Drive, Brighton,
OL,17,Fadmitted causing serious injury by
OL,18,Fdangerous driving at a hearing at
OL,19,FWorthing Magistrates' Court.
