OL,7,FHe was sentenced at Lewes Crown Court
OL,8,Fto two years and four months in prison
OL,9,Fand was disqualified from driving for
OL,10,Ffour years and four months.
OL,12,FThe court was told how the incident
OL,13,Fhappened at 12.10pm on 13 December
OL,14,F2023 on the A27 at Southbourne.
OL,16,FCole failed to see the hazard ahead of
OL,17,Fhim on a long, straight stretch of
OL,18,Froad, as dashcam footage showed he was
OL,19,Fdistracted on his phone.
