OL,7,FThe Volkswagen van he was driving
OL,8,Fcollided with a Peugeot car which had
OL,9,Fbroken down.
OL,11,FThe driver of the car, a man in his
OL,12,F60s from Hampshire, was struck
OL,13,Fdirectly by the van and was taken to
OL,14,Fhospital.
OL,16,FThe victim's family said his injuries
OL,17,Fand treatment are a "daily reminder of
OL,18,Fa tragedy that has reshaped every
OL,19,Faspect of our lives".
